Electronic Equipment, Instruments and Components

Company Overview of ACE Energy Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
ACE Energy Inc. manufactures energy-efficient lighting solutions and power management resources for use in banks, retail stores, office buildings, classrooms, dormitories, hotels, and other facilities. The company offers SMARTAutomation solutions, which include building automation and controls for heating, ventilating, and air conditioning, energy, lighting, video security, fire, life safety, and other functions; SMARTLight program that provide energy saving lighting and control solutions for facilities; and SMART METER program that offers a metering system, Demandtrak, an open source Web based platform for customers to view multiple energy uses and utilization aspects of their facilities. I...
ACE Energy Inc. manufactures energy-efficient lighting solutions and power management resources for use in banks, retail stores, office buildings, classrooms, dormitories, hotels, and other facilities. The company offers SMARTAutomation solutions, which include building automation and controls for heating, ventilating, and air conditioning, energy, lighting, video security, fire, life safety, and other functions; SMARTLight program that provide energy saving lighting and control solutions for facilities; and SMART METER program that offers a metering system, Demandtrak, an open source Web based platform for customers to view multiple energy uses and utilization aspects of their facilities. It also provides SMARTSense AX certification technical training course for systems integrators, OEMs, other business partners, and distributors, as well as end-user customers; and energy efficient lighting upgrades, building and facility automation, metering solutions, and heating and cooling controls; and consulting, analysis, design, and turnkey solutions for businesses. The company is based in Princeton, New Jersey.
Detailed Description


211 Carnegie CenterPrinceton, NJ 08540United States



Phone: 609-524-4500

www.aceenergy.com







