Professional Resources

DEDICATED TO HELPING YOU GROW
In addition to our portfolio of science-based continuing education options and Specialist Programs created to better serve your target markets, ACE has a number of professional resources dedicated to helping you grow. We offer insight on the latest training techniques, research and industry news through our monthly digital publication, Certified™. We evaluate the effectiveness of products, programs and trends with independent research we commission from university partners. We’ve secured a number of professional discounts with industry partners. And we offer guided, easy-to-follow lifestyle programs and thousands of other tools your clients can utilize on ACEfit.com.Learn More »
 



 













































